column2: SELECT TOP #  G.ra,G.dec,G.modelMag_r,G.modelMagErr_r,G.extinction_r,  sp.z,sp.zErr,  G.modelFlux_u,  G.modelFlux_g,  G.modelFlux_r,  G.modelFlux_i,  G.modelFlux_z,  G.modelFluxIvar_u,G.modelFluxIvar_g,G.modelFluxIvar_r,G.modelFluxIvar_i,G.modelFluxIvar_z,GN.distance  FROM  dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN  JOIN Galaxy AS G ON GN.objID = G.objID  JOIN PhotoTag AS pt ON pt.objID = G.objID  JOIN specPhoto AS sp ON GN.objID = sp.objID  ORDER by distance
